{
  "stem": "24364.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it-- we were told after that that it had been an act of sabotage, because they didn't want-- they had found out that they were going to be deported and they tried to avoid that by somehow wrecking the engines, because they knew that shipwrecked people usually are not being deported, or can't be deported, because there is such a law.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so the-- the Haganah in Israel had prepared for that sabotage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unfortunately, they didn't do it very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And instead of blowing up only the engines, they blew up part of the boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were supposed to do it when all the people are on deck so that nobody would get hurt and people could get into life boats or jump into the water and something, and only part of the ship would be wrecked.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I guess the bomb was too big or whatever they did just was too much.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so about 300-odd people died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the Haganah was the sort of pseudo-military organization of Zionists.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were clandestine at that time, because of the British, obviously.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, after a couple of days, we were all transported to Atlit, which was a camp in Israel which usually served as a quarantine for the immigrants.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- actually, we got to-- to Atlit and were put into huts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And actually, we were in a hut-- a friend of mine and I were in a hut together with the people from the rather than our people, just by pure chance.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was quite pleasant to be with other people, because we had been with the people from the Czech transport for so long.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite pleasant to be with somebody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
